The Maven Unit and Integration Test Guide (MaUI Test Guide)

  This will be the place to find information about how to
  do unit and integration tests in {{{http://maven.apache.org}Maven}} projects.

  This is no plugin etc. it's only a guide how to do different things with {{{http://maven.apache.org}Maven}}.

* Overview

  This guide is separated into two big chapters where the first is about
  {{{./unit-test.html}Unit Testing with Maven}} and the second about
  {{{./integration-test.html}Integration Testing with Maven}}.


